Welcome to San Francisco, the city by the bay and to Sheraton the Gateway to this beautiful city!<br><br>

<b>Sheraton Gateway Hotel</b><br>
600 Airport Boulevard<br>
Burlingame CA 94010<br>
tel: (650) 340-8500<br>
<A HREF="http://www.mapquest.com/maps/map.adp?address=600+Airport+Blvd&city=Burlingame&state=CA&zipcode=94010&country=US&cid=lfmaplink">MapQuest Map</A><br><br>

<div align="center"><img src="images/map.gif" width="300" height="241" border="1" alt=""></div>

<h2>General Directions</h2>

<h3>From North</h3>
Proceed southbound on US Highway 101. Travel past San Francisco Airport to the Broadway/Burlingame Exit. Take the second right and travel over the freeway overpass to the other side of the freeway. At the first light turn right and at the next light, turn left onto Airport Boulevard. The hotel will be approximately one mile ahead.

<h3>From South</h3>
Travel northbound on US Highway 101. Exit onto Anza Boulevard. Turn right at the traffic light onto Airport Boulevard. The hotel is approximately one quarter mile ahead and on the left. <!-- The hotel is located at the intersection of Anza Boulevard and Airport Boulevard. -->

<h3>From East</h3>
Take Highway 80 East to Highway 101 South. Proceed southbound on US Highway 101. Travel past San Francisco Airport to the Broadway/Burlingame Exit. Take the second right and travel over the freeway overpass to the other side of the freeway. At the first light turn right and at the next light, turn left onto Airport Boulevard. The hotel will be approximately one mile ahead.

<h3><a name="bart">BART</a></h3>
<a href="http://www.bart.gov/index.asp" target="_blank">BART (Bay Area Rapid Transit System)</a> now offers train service to the San Francisco International Airport from many bay area cities. Flying in to Oakland International Airport but need to stay close to businesses in the Silicon Area then stay with us and take BART from the Oakland Airport to San Francisco Airport and we will pick you up. Our courtesy airport shuttle will bring you from the San Francisco International Airport BART station to our doorsteps!<br><br>

Visit <a href="http://www.bart.gov/index.asp" target="_blank">BART's website</a> for schedules and fares.

